           <h3>ABOUT US</h3>
           <p>
               <b>Afrocheck</b>
                is a dynamic streetwear brand that works together with the JOKA charity foundation to help support needy, sick and poor communities in parts of Africa.
               Our dream is to build water pumps for clean drinking water, libraries and community shelters for poor neighborhoods in some parts of Africa.
               Afrocheck is Changing the Narrative of Streetwear, Connecting Culture through People, Art and Fashion.
               Every item you purchase on our website, sends <b>1 Euro</b> to the JOKA Foundation to save lives.
           </p>
           <p>
                We are very serious about the overall shopping experience for all our customers from the quality of our website to the after sales service for
               customers require that extra bit of care.
           </p>
           <p>
                To ensure that the quality of our product, we examine each product before they are shipped out to the customer.
               Our products been all 100% cotton and well tested, we have the ability,
