           </p>
           <h3>Shipping Information</h3>
           <p>
               While we endeavor to ship all orders placed before 2 PM the next business day, we cannot guarantee this, especially during promotional periods.
               You will receive an email once your order has been created; this email will include your order number along with tracking information.
               Please remember that all tracking numbers take a few hours (and sometimes up to 24 hours) to become active from the point of notification.
               This is because of the time delay between us packing and shipping an item and our delivery couriers updating their systems.
           </p>
           <h3>Return and Refund Policy</h3>
           <p>
               If you need to return an item, enter a claim in our About Us page within 30 days of purchase and we will email you back with further instructions.
               We do not refund purchases, however, if you are not satisfied with your order, you may return it for store credit which can be used future purchases.
           </p>
